defaultBPS is the primary UK learned society concerned with research into drugs and the way they work. Our members work in a
defaultcademia, industry, and the health services, and many are medically qualified. The Society covers the whole spectrum of pharmacology, including laboratory, clinical, toxicological and regulatory aspects. 
defaultClinic
defaultal pharmacology is the medical speciality
default dedi
defaultcated to promoting safe and effective use of medicines for patient benefit. Clinical pharmacologists work as consultants in the NHS and many hold prominent positions in UK Universities.
